thread.title_full: Ticketebo reviewed by About the Book Merimbula

author: About the Book Merimbula
title: About the Book Merimbula
text: We used ticketebo for a recent small one-day event. The set-up process was simple and the result was seamless. I received good freedback from event attendees, who described the purchasing experience as easy and efficient. Ticketebo staff gave us great support and dealt with our requests straight away. The daily reporting service was very helpful too. I will use ticketebo again and recommend to anyone planning an event. It certainly was "pain free!
